n someone who is a special client, need tip on every order client, invoice page.\r\nSolution: Client notes should be on the top of every page for that client.\r\n\r\n* Business plan bundle request\r\n* Overdue VOIP summary page\r\n* Overdue Morden summary page\r\n* VOIP number customer field suck as do you want to keep your number, Current ISP, new number request.\r\n* Tracking every page the staff working on. If a customer complain and one staff open without reply to it, we can tracking the fault.\r\n* Transfer money from the one invoice to another, if the invoice is over paid the money should auto goes to the credit and the credit should auto apply to the next available or the select invoices.\r\n* Manual Invoice overdue won’t suspend the account, all the account should suspended when there is an overdue invoice. \r\n* Optimise the searching result.\r\nExample: when you try to search 1111, it shows order 1111, account 1111, invoice 1111, transection 1111 etc. The staff has to look at the every single one to locate the details.\r\nSolution: give a range from different types of data, for example client id has 5 digits. Order with 6 digits. \r\n* Ticket queue order currently is by staff last update, should be client last update.\r\n* Cancelation request queue and process status need to be added.\r\n* Customer reply from top to bottom.\r\n* Notes detail need more logs, staff can delete the note, and when can’t see what they did.\r\n* Transfer account from one to another one\r\nExample: current we experience 5/w, to transfer the ownership the staff has to manually do a new order, and fill the details and transfer the account.\r\nSolution: Form on the website and back to do a single click transfer.\r\n\r\n* Name Issue.\r\nPeople putting combine names and partner name, will that affected debit collection.\r\nWe can either enable put more than one names, like add more name option.\r\n* Reasonable due date, the due date should only be 1 year from today\r\n* Ticket priority log keyword \r\n* Ticket read status, when client read the tickets, the ticket should stay the client reading status, if the ticket without read by client the staff should call back to request addition details to continue process the order\r\n* Everyone should have todo list and notes tracking on the RA.',NULL,NULL,1,36,4,NULL,4,1,'2017-01-14 13:32:23','2018-02-09 11:48:54','2017-01-14',0,NULL,NULL,1747,1,2,0,NULL),(1754,1,50,'HB->RA Migration','Pseudocode:\r\n\r\n* For each client\r\n** Use API to pull details; insert into tblclients\r\n** For each note associated with the client (from hb_notes)\r\n*** Insert into tblnotes',NULL,NULL,5,4,4,NULL,4,3,'2017-01-24 12:45:48','2017-03-13 17:27:40','2017-01-24',0,NULL,NULL,1754,1,2,0,'2017-03-13 17:27:40'),(1777,1,50,'Flowchart invoice/payment workflow','',NULL,NULL,6,4,6,NULL,4,1,'2017-03-01 15:41:40','2017-03-13 18:11:20','2017-03-01',0,NULL,NULL,1777,1,2,0,'2017-03-13 18:11:20'),(1790,2,50,'Improved Notes System','*DRAFT*\r\n\r\nCan be applied against:\r\n* Client Profiles\r\n\r\nWith the following properties:\r\n* id (autoincrement)\r\n* userid (client profile to assign to)\r\n* adminid (id of the creating admin)\r\n* assignto (?)\r\n* flag (id of the admin it\'s assigned to)\r\n* created (auto datetime)\r\n* duedate (datetime, editable)\r\n* modified (auto datetime)\r\n* note (actual contents)\r\n* sticky (whether to show on profile or not)','2017-04-30',NULL,1,4,4,NULL,4,4,'2017-03-07 15:20:13','2018-02-09 11:48:54','2017-03-07',0,NULL,NULL,1790,1,2,0,NULL),(1826,1,50,'Client Invoice View','Find out by reading code, difference of Draft, invoice status, what it’s used for, what automation currently does WHMCS use it for? I think Draft is our change, or your change? Cant tell as it’s not in normal WHMCS, if we addon the feature we have to comment what the future does, how it’s used.','2017-05-11',NULL,5,4,4,NULL,4,1,'2017-05-08 09:37:41','2017-05-08 12:47:45','2017-05-08',0,NULL,NULL,1826,1,2,0,'2017-05-08 12:47:45')